Package commands

package commands
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BasicCommand
    Abstract class for all the commands.
    ClearCommand
    Command to clear the collection.
    CountLessThanCharacterCommand
    Outputs amount of elements in which character field contains value less than given
    ExecuteScriptCommand
    Command that is used to execute scripts.
    ExitCommand
    Some sort of wrapper for System.exit(0).
    HelpCommand
    Command that outputs name and description for all the commands in its CommandManager.
    InfoCommand
    Command, that briefly takes basic info from the CollectionManager and ouputs it into console.
    InsertCommand
    Command that is used for adding some stuff in collection.
    PrintAscendingCommand
    Outputs all the elements stored in its CollectionManager in ascending order
    PrintFieldDescendingTypeCommand
    Outputs id : type
    RemoveGreaterCommand
    Removes greater elements (gets initial element by id)
    RemoveGreaterKeyCommand
    Removes elements with key greater than this one
    RemoveKeyCommand
    Removes element by key.
    ReplaceIfLowerCommand
    Replaces all the elements that are lower
    SaveCommand
    Used to save something to file.
    ShowCommand
    Shows the collection
    UpdateCommand
    Used for updating element with specific id
